timesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdid-epstein-accuser-virginia-giuffre-indeed-meet-an-accident-family-says-%2Farticleshow%2F119909151.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdid-epstein-accuser-virginia-giuffre-indeed-meet-an-accident-family-says-%2Famp_articleshow%2F119909151.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdid-epstein-accuser-virginia-giuffre-indeed-meet-an-accident-family-says-%2Famp_articleshow%2F119909151.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCan't%20Donate%20Someone%20Else's%20Property%2C%26quot%3B%20Says%20Amit%20Shah%20On%20Waqf%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20speaking%20at%20the%20debate%20over%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20this%20evening%2C%20presented%20a%20long%20list%20of%20properties%20that%20he%20said%20were%20given%20for%20Waqf.%20The%20list%20included%20land%20belonging%20to%20temples%2C%20land%20belonging%20to%20other%20religions%2C%20the%20%C2%A0government%20and%20others.%20His%20point%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20donate%20someone%20else's%20property.%20You%20donate%20something%20which%20is%20yours%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20reinforcement%20of%20the%20government's%20contention%20that%20major%20lands%20and%20properties%20almost%20went%20to%20Waqf%20but%20for%20last-minute%20saves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20to%20stop%20grabbing%20of%20602%20sq%20km%20by%20Waqf.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProperties%20in%20(Delhi's)%20Lutyens%20zone%20went%20to%20Waqf%2C%20and%20they%20started%20taking%20over%20government%20land...%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20a%20400-year-old%20temple%20property%20was%20declared%20as%20Waqf's.%20Land%20for%20a%205-star%20establishment%20was%20given%20to%20Waqf%20for%2012%2C000%20a%20month...%20Several%20properties%20belong