%20TGIIC%20had%20to%20follow%20the%20top%20court's%20orders%3B%20i.e.%2C%20constitute%20of%20a%20committee%20to%20oversee%20the%20felling%20of%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecifically%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20ruled%20that%20if%20the%20land%20was%20inhabited%20by%20wildlife%20the%20committee%20would%20have%20to%20study%20the%20impact%20of%20felling%20of%20trees%20for%20a%20month%20before%20reaching%20a%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20claimed%20the%20land%20in%20question%20is%20home%20to%20many%20species%20of%20animals%20and%20birds%20and%2C%20accordingly%2C%20the%20Vata%20Foundation%2C%20a%20non-governmental%20organisation%2C%20sought%20deemed%20forest%20status%20and%20demanded%20it%20be%20declared%20a%20'national%20park'%20under%20the%20Wildlife%20(Protection)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Advocate-General%20Sudershan%20Reddy%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Telangana%20government%2C%20told%20the%20court%20the%20400%20acres%20is%20not%20recognised%20as%20a%20'forest'%2C%20a%20fact%20he%20stressed%20by%20pointing%20out%20high-rise%20buildings%20-%20with%20four%20helipads%20-%20had%20been%20built%20on%20adjacent%20parcels.%20He%20also%20argued%20that%20several%20areas%20in%20Hyderabad%20had%20snakes%20and%20peacocks%2C%20all%20of%20which%20could%20not%20be%20declared%20'forests'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20both%20sides%2C%20the%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20High%20Court%2C%20led%20by%20Acting%20Chief%20Justice%20Sujoy%20Paul%2C%20ordered%20ongoing%20work%20be%20stopped%20till%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUniversity%20students%20had%20launched%20a%20protest%20after%20the%20TGIIC%20began%20the%20work%20to%20clear%20the%20land%20of%20trees%20and%20rocks%20for%20its%20auction%20for%20the%20development%20of%20IT%20parks.%20The%20students%20have%20announced%20an%20indefinite%20boycott%20of%20classes%20until%20their%20demands%20are%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20escalated%20Sunday%20when%20bulldozers%20arrived%20to%20flatten%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20confrontation%20ensued%20and%20the%20students%20were%20thrashed%20by%20the%20police%2C%20who%20accused%20them%20of%20obstructing%20government%20officials%20from%20doing%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Telangana%20government%20has%20clarified%20it%20has%20not%20taken%20land%20belonging%20to%20the%20university%2C%20and%20criticised%20the%20opposition%20BRS%20and%20BJP%20for%20spreading%20lies%20about%20the%20land%20for%20political%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStringent%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20those%20obstructing%20development%2C%20the%20state%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20entry%20into%20the%20matter%20widened%20the%20political%20row%20after%20the%20BRS%20accused%20the%20police%20of%20manhandling%20the%20protesting%20students.%20The%20BRS%20had%20earlier%20attacked%20the%20Congress%2C%20accusing%20its%20top%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20of%20spreading%20hatred%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20'Mohabbat%20ki%20Dukaan'.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743599160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fujsrfqlo_hyderabad-university-tension_625x300_31_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-court-halts-all-work-on-disputed-land-near-hyderabad-university-8070093%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Telangana%20High%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20halted%20-%20for%2024%20hours%20-%20work%20on%20400%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20Kancha%20Gachibowli%2C%20which%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20row%20after%20students%20protesting%20against%20redevelopment%20clashed%20with%20cops.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Game%20changer'%3A%20UFC%20Boss%20Dana%20White%20announces%20partnership%20with%20Meta%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743599054000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2F