229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Lakshmi%20searched%20for%20better%20alternatives%2C%20the%20larger%20menstrual%20health%20space%20was%20also%20shifting.%20Arunachalam%20Muruganantham%2C%20now%20widely%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Padman%E2%80%99%2C%20began%20developing%20affordable%20disposable%20pads.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20menstrual%20cup%20%E2%80%94%20marketed%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98She%20Cup%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20was%20gaining%20attention%20in%20urban%20circles.%20But%20Lakshmi%20remained%20cautious.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20not%20very%20comfortable%20with%20the%20menstrual%20cup%20for%20my%20rural%20adolescents.%20The%20wearer%20has%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20place%20and%20wear%20it.%20If%20they%20have%20medical%20issues%2C%20there%20is%20no%20access%20to%20gynaecologists%20in%20rural%20areas.%20So%2C%20Jatan%20Sansthan%20has%20not%20promoted%20menstrual%20cups.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20design%20meant%20to%20be%20copied%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20this%20concern%20that%20led%20to%20Project%20Uger%20in%202011.%20%E2%80%98Uger%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20which%20means%20%E2%80%98new%20beginning%E2%80%99%20in%20Mewari%20%E2%80%94%20introduced%20one%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20reusable%20menstrual%20pads%2C%20developed%20by%20Lakshmi%20while%20pursuing%20her%20PhD%20at%20IIT%20Bombay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20anxious%20to%20make%20a%20pad%20that%20would%20work%20for%20women%20and%20girls%20who%20had%20started%20wearing%20underwear.%20The%20Uger%20pad%20is%20made%20entirely%20of%20cotton%20and%20is%20biodegradable%20within%20three%20to%20four%20months.%20It%20has%20straps%20so%20you%20can%20fix%20any%20cloth%20inside.%20A%20set%20of%20six%20costs%20Rs%20180%20and%20lasts%20three%20months.%20The%20insert%20cloth%20is%20extra%2C%E2%80%9D%