nage%20their%20tax%20credits%20and%20incentives%20(C%26amp%3BI).%20The%20startup%20uses%20AI%20to%20find%20applicable%20benefits%20based%20on%20a%20company's%20background%20and%20location%2C%20and%20it%20manages%20the%20application%20process%20and%20timeline%20for%20a%20company's%20entire%20C%26amp%3BI%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncentify%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fryan-tax-viacom-cbs-cargill-technology-incentify-pitch-deck-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%3C%2Fa%3E%20%244.25%20million%20in%202020%2C%20and%20its%20clients%20include%20KPMG%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Cargill%2C%20and%20investor%20Ryan%20LLC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncentify%20CEO%20Laurence%20Sotsky%20said%20that%20adding%20AI%20to%20the%20platform%20%E2%80%94%20namely%2C%20Incentify's%20Explore%20tool%2C%20which%20is%20where%20companies%20get%20personalized%20tax%20incentives%20%E2%80%94%20has%20helped%20the%20startup%20supercharge%20its%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20create%20Explore%2C%20we%20compiled%20every%20federal%2C%20state%2C%20and%20local%20grant%2C%20credit%2C%20abatement%2C%20and%20incentive%20into%20a%20massive%20data%20warehouse%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20then%20trained%20our%20AI%20model%20on%20this%20vast%20dataset%2C%20enabling%20us%20to%20deliver%20unparalleled%20insights%20and%20rich%20content%20to%20our%20customers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESotksy%20added%20that%20Incentify's%20business%20model%20was%20a%20tough%20sell%20for%20some%20VCs%20during%20the%20fundraising%20process.%20In%20addition%20to%20traditional%20SaaS%20revenue%2C%20Incentify%20also%20earns%20a%20fee%20when%20it%20connects%20customers%20with%20a%20network%20of%20advisor%20partners%20that%20it%20maintains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInterestingly%2C%20the%20larger%20the%20VC%2C%20the%20harder%20it%20seemed%20for%20them%20to%20fit%20us%20into%20their%20investment%20thesis%2C%26quot%3B%20Sotksy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20an