-ranking-2020-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIHOP%20pancakes%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20good.%20They%20were%20fluffy%2C%20yet%20dense%20(maybe%20substantial%20is%20a%20better%20word%3F)%20with%20a%20rich%20buttermilk%20flavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wouldn't%20say%20they're%20%3Cem%3Egreat%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20lump%20of%20butter%20heaped%20onto%20their%20top%20makes%20the%20center%20too%20mushy%20if%20left%20to%20sit%20too%20long%20%E2%80%94%20but%20they're%20definitely%20worth%20ordering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bacon%20was%20pretty%20tasty%2C%20too.%20It%20was%20crisp%20in%20some%20bits%20but%20not%20dried%20out%20and%20still%20had%20that%20pleasant%20chewiness%20in%20the%20thicker%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20wish%20the%20sunny-side-up%20eggs%20had%20been%20cooked%20longer.%20They%20felt%20watery%20and%20didn't%20look%20or%20taste%20great.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20my%20daughter%20happily%20chowed%20down%20on%20pancakes%2C%20my%20son%2C%20who%20is%20quite%20the%20foodie%2C%20took%20one%20look%20at%20the%20spread%20out%20before%20us%20and%20decided%20he'd%20wait%20to%20eat%20until%20we%20got%20home.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECautiously%20optimistic%2C%20I%20carried%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20house%20scramble%20was%20OK.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hashbrown%20and%20omelet%20at%20IHOP%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dc73a169253ccddf99e0d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20wasn't%20blown%20away%20by%20the%20hash%20browns%20or%20house%20scramble.%3Cp%3ESteven%20John%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIHOP's%20house%20scramble%20was%20decent%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20seem%20to%20be%20cooked%20consistently%20throughout.%20It%20contained%20a%20decent%20amount%20of%20bacon%2C%20but%20some%20bites%20were%20wetter%20than%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hash%20browns%20it%20came%20with%20didn't%20taste%20like%20much%20of%20