ed-foods-rules-to-stop-overeating-simple-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shah%20Bano%20To%20Shayara%20Bano%3A%20BJP's%20History%20Attack%20On%20Congress%20In%20Waqf%20Debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShah%20Bano%20and%20Shayara%20Bano%2C%20whose%20legal%20battles%20led%20to%20landmark%20court%20judgments%20for%20Muslim%20women's%20rights%2C%20found%20mention%20in%20parliament%20today%20as%20the%20BJP%20countered%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%20against%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20to%20change%20rules%20governing%20Muslim%20charitable%20properties.%20Defending%20the%20Bill%2C%20BJP%20veteran%20Ravi%20Shankar%20Prasad%20slammed%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi-led%20Congress%20government's%20decision%20to%20bring%20a%20law%20that%20nullified%20the%20Shah%20Bano%20judgment%2C%20and%20also%20accused%20the%20UPA%20government%20of%20delaying%20its%20response%20in%20triple%20talaq%20case.%20The%20Congress%20had%20not%20recovered%20electorally%20since%20it%20%26quot%3Bbowed%20down%26quot%3B%20to%20conservative%20sections%20after%20the%20Shah%20Bano%20verdict%2C%20Mr%20Prasad%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Shah%20Bano%20Judgment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndore's%20Shah%20Bano%20Begum%20had%20been%20divorced%20by%20her%20husband%2C%20Mohd%20Ahmad%20Khan%2C%20in%201978.%20She%20approached%20the%20court%20seeking%20maintenance%20from%20her%20husband%20after%20he%20had%20divorced%20her.%20Her%20husband%20argued%20that%20as%20a%20Muslim%2C%20he%20was%20only%20obliged%20to%20pay%20maintenance%20during%20the%20'iddat'%20period%20--%20about%20three%20months%20after%20divorce%20--%20and%20not%20after%20that.%20The%20question%20then%20became%20whether%20Shah%20Bano%2C%20as%20a%20Muslim%20woman%2C%20could%20claim%20maintenance%20under%20Section%20125%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%2C%20under%20which%20a%20man%20with%20sufficient%20means%20has%20to%20pay%20maintenance%20to%20his%20wife%20who%20cannot%20maintain%20herself.%20In%201985%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20Shah%20Bano%20and%20said%20a%20woman%20who%20is%20unable%20to%20maintain%20herself%20is%20entitled%20to%20take%20recourse%20to%20Section%20125%20of%20the%20CrPC.%20The%20court%20noted%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20conflict%20between%20the%20provisions%20of%20section%20125%20and%20those%20of%20the%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20on%20the%20question%20of%20the%20husband's%20obligation%20to%20provide%20maintenance%20for%20a%20divorced%20wife%20who%20is%20unable%20to%20maintain%20herself%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Government's%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20recorded%20a%20landslide%20victory%20in%20the%201984%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20held%20shortly%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20assassination%2C%20winning%20404%20seats%20--%20the%20highest%20ever%20tally%20in%20a%20general%20election.%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20was%20a%20year%20into%20his%20Prime%20Ministerial%20term%20when%20the%20Shah%20Bano%20judgment%20emerged.%20A%20section%20within%20the%20Congress%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20warned%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20may%20harm%20the%20Congress%20politically%2C%20as%20Muslims%20may%20see%20it%20as%20an%20encroachment%20on%20personal%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20subsequently%20brought%20the%20Muslim%20Women%20(Protection%20of%20Rights%20on%20Divorce)%20Act%2C%20which%20effectively%20nullified%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict.%20This%20law%20shifted%20the%20burden%20of%20providing%20maintenance%20to%20the%20family%20of%20a%20divorced%20woman%20and%20said%20the%20husband%20is%20obliged%20to%20pay%20only%20during%20the%20iddat%20period%20--%20about%20three%20months%20after%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20rivals%20have%20repeatedly%20referenced%20the%20case%20to%20attack%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party%20over%20what%20they%20call%20%26quot%3Bvotebank%20politics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Shayara%20Bano%20Case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShayara%20Bano%20and%20Rizwan%20Ahmed%20married%20in%202002%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20couple%20had%20a%20son%20and%20a%20daughter.%20In%202015%2C%20Rizwan%20Ahmed%20divorced%20Shayara%20Bano%20with%20talaq-e-biddat%20or%20triple%20talaq%20--%20a%20practice%20in%20which%20the%20husband%20can%20divorce%20his%20wife%20by%20uttering%20the%20word%20talaq%20(divorce)%20thrice.%20This%20practice%20does%20not%20require%20the%20wife's%20consent.%20Shayara%20Bano%20contended%20that%20triple%20talaq%20violates%20a%20woman's%20fundamental%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20a%20five-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20barred%20the%20triple%20talaq%20practice%20by%20a%203-2%20majority.%20The%20majority%20view%20held%20that%20the%20practice%20was%20not%20an%20essential%20element%20of%20Islam%20and%20described%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bmanifestly%20arbitrary%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20the%20marital%20tie%20can%20be%20broken%20capriciously%20and%20whimsically%20by%20a%20Muslim%20man%20without%20any%20attempt%20at%20reconciliation%20to%20save%20it%26quot%3B.%20The%20court%20ruled%20that%20this%20practice%20violates%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20equality%20before%20law%20under%20Article%2014%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20It%20also%20directed%20the%20government%20to%20bring%20a%20law%20to%20regulate%20divorce%20among%20Muslims.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20brought%20the%20Muslim%20Women%20(Protection%20of%20Rights%20on%20Marriage)%20Act%2C%202019%2C%20criminalising%20triple%20talaq.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERavi%20Shankar%20Prasad's%20Attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%201985%20Shah%20Bano%20judgment%2C%20Mr%20Prasad%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20votebank%20politics.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20Shah%20Bano%20case%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20that%20she%20should%20get%20a%20few%20hundred%20rupees.%20There%20was%20an%20uproar.%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20was%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20with%20a%20majority%20of%20400%20seats.%20I%20want%20to%20talk%20about%20my%20friend%20(now%20Bihar%20governor)%20Arif%20Mohammed%20Khan%2C%20a%20minister%20in%20that%20government.%20He%20had%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20verdict%20is%20good.%20But%20then%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20was%20rattled%20and%20told%20him%20a%20law%20is%20being%20brought%20to%20overturn%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20to%20the%20triple%20talaq%20case%2C%20he%20alleged%20that%20the%20UPA%20government%20did%20not%20file%20replies%20for%20two%20years%20to%20keep%20the%20matter%20in%20limbo.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20our%20government%20came%20in%202014%2C%20I%20was%20Law%20Minister.%20Prime%20Minister%20(Narendra%20Modi)%20told%20me%20to%20tell%20the%20court%20that%20the%20government%20is%20against%20triple%20talaq%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20Congress%2C%20Mr%20Prasad%20questioned%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20far%20will%20the%20country%20go%20for%20vote%20bank%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20veteran%20said%20since%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20won%20400%20seats%20in%20the%201984%20election%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20never%20won%20a%20majority%20on%20its%20own.%20%26quot%3BHe%20bowed%20down%20in%20the%20Shah%20Bano%20case.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20not%20won%20a%20majority%2C%20remember%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Waqf%20Bill%20Row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20amend%20the%201995%20law%20governing%20Waqf%20properties%2C%20aims%20to%20improve%20the%20management%20of%20Waqf%20properties%20in%20India%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20and%20other%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20opposed%20the%20legislation.%20They%20have%20said%20that%20the%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20set%20up%20to%20examine%20the%20Bill%20did%20not%20consider%20Opposition%20MPs'%20suggestions.%20They%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20government%20is%20rushing%20ahead%20with%20the%20Bill%20and%20that%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20target%20the%20minorities%20to%20gain%20electorally%20from%20polarisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20accused%20the%20Opposition%20of%20playing%20vote%20bank%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743594240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fjeia5mh8_shah-bano_625x300_02_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-shah-bano-to-shayara-bano-bjps-history-attack-on-congress-in-waqf-debate-8069736%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shah%20Bano%20and%20Shayara%20Bano%2C%20whose%20legal%20battles%20led%20to%20landmark%20court%20judgments%20for%20Muslim%20women's%20rights%2C%20found%20a%20mention%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%20as%20the%20BJP%20countered%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%20against%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-shah-bano-to-shayara-bano-bjps-history-attack-on-congress-in-waqf-debate-8069736%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%3A%20Why%20Muslims%20are%20opposing%20it%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743593989000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119906251%2Cimgsize-880252.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-why-muslims-are-opposing-it%2Farticleshow%2F119905795.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Muslim%20leaders%20and%20organizations%20object%20to%20the%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%20asserting%20it%20threatens%20the%20autonomy%20of%20Waqf%20properties%20dedicated%20for%20religious%20and%20charitable%20purposes.%20They%20claim%20the%20Bill%20aims%20to%20seize%20such%20lands%20and%20hampers%20Muslim%20religious%20liberties%2C%20labeling%20it%20as%20deceptive%20and%20unconstitutional.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akhilesh%20Yadav%20Jabs%20BJP%20Over%20Delay%20In%20Choosing%20Chief%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20Replies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%20witnessed%20a%20banter%20between%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20after%20the%20latter%20fired%20a%20barb%20at%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20for%20its%20delay%20in%20electing%20a%20party%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20House%20during%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20the%20BJP%20was%20facing%20infighting%20as%20leaders%20compete%20to%20prove%20who%20the%20%26quot%3Bworse%20Hindu%26quot%3B%20is.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20saying%20this%20just%20like%20that.%20The%20party%2C%20which%20claims%20to%20be%20the%20world's%20largest%20party%2C%20could%20not%20elect%20its%20national%20president%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20stood%20up%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAkhilesh%20ji%20said%20something%20with%20a%20smile.%20And%20I%20will%20respond%20with%20a%20smile.%26quot%3B%20Pointing%20to%20the%20Opposition%20benches%2C%20the%20Home%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20the%20parties%20there%20have%20to%20elect%20their%20national%20president%20from%20among%20five%20people%20of%20the%20family.%20We%20must%20follow%20a%20process%20and%20choose%20a%20chief%20from%2012-13%20crore%20members.%20So%20it%20takes%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said%2C%20drawing%20a%20big%20cheer%20from%20BJP%20MPs.%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-live-updates-waqf-discussion-today-india-bloc-to-vote-against-bill-8066548%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EClick%20Here%20For%20Parliament%20Live%20Updates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20Mr%20Yadav%2C%20the%20BJP%20veteran%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20won't%20take%20time.%20I%20am%20telling%20you%2C%20you%20will%20be%20party%20president%20for%2025%20years.%20No%20one%20can%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20responded%20with%20a%20smile%20and%20added%20a%20jab.%20%26quot%3BThe%20yatra%20held%20a%20few%20days%20back%2C%20was%20it%20a%20yatra%20to%20mark%20the%2075-year%20extension%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20remark%20was%20widely%20seen%20as%20a%20reference%20to%20the%2075%20years-age%20rule%20for%20senior%20BJP%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%2C%20who%20represents%20Kannauj%2C%20said%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20has%20been%20brought%20to%20%26quot%3Bcover%20the%20government's%20many%20failures%26quot%3B%2C%20including%20demonetisation%2C%20unemployment%20and%20price%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20country%20has%20a%20mixed%20culture.%20You%20are%20saying%20we%20have%20introduced%20two%20women%20members%20to%20Waqf%20board.%20I%20will%20see%20how%20many%20women%20get%20BJP%20tickets%20in%20the%20Bihar%20election.%20BJP%20is%20talking%20about%20identifying%20Muslim%20brothers'%20land%20under%20Waqf%20so%20that%20they%20can%20draw%20a%20curtain%20across%20Hindu%20brothers%20who%20died%20or%20went%20missing%20at%20the%20Kumbh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20should%20tell%20us%20the%20names%20of%2030%20people%20who%20died%20there%20and%20about%20the%201%2C000%20who%20went%20missing.%20Where%20is%20the%20list%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20said%20the%20land%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20China%20has%20set%20up%20villages%26quot%3B%20is%20more%20important%20than%20Waqf%20land.%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20must%20guarantee%20that%20no%20Waqf%20land%20would%20be%20used%20for%20any%20other%20pu