%20scores%20of%201%2C%2029%20and%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaiswal%20has%20been%20facing%20a%20lot%20of%20problems%20during%20the%20powerplay%20since%20the%20IPL%202024%2C%20particularly%20the%20first%20three%20overs.%20Since%20the%20last%20IPL%2C%20he%20has%20been%20dismissed%20eight%20out%20of%2018%20times%20within%20the%20first%20three%20overs%20of%20an%20innings.%20This%20is%20a%2044%20per%20cent%20dismissal%20rate.%20It%20is%20up%20from%20the%2029%20per%20cent%20dismissal%20rate%20across%20seasons%202022%20and%202023%2C%20with%20the%20batter%20smashing%20625%20runs%20in%20the%20latter%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%202024%20season%20was%20an%20underwhelming%20for%20Jaiswal%2C%20as%20he%20did%20score%20435%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2031.07%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20almost%20156%2C%20but%20he%20could%20score%20just%20one%20century%20and%20fifty%20in%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20interesting%20to%20note%20that%20his%20attacking%20shot%20percentage%20has%20gone%20down%20to%2070%20per%20cent%20over%20last%20two%20seasons%20as%20compared%20to%20previous%20two%20seasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20Inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743592800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fc4e0k2j8_yashasvi-jaiswal-bcci_625x300_02_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fyashasvi-jaiswal-quits-mumbai-submits-application-to-change-team-report-8068403%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20opening%20batter%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20has%20reportedly%20decided%20to%20change%20his%20state%20team.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A43%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fyashasvi-jaiswal-quits-mumbai-submits-application-to-change-team-report-8068403%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arnold%20Schwarzenegger%20To%20Jerry%20Seinfeld%2C%20New%20B