PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20has%20written%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20seeking%20his%20personal%20intervention%20to%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%20which%20was%20introduced%20in%20parliament%20today%20for%20debate%20and%20passing.%20All%20the%20non-NDA%20parties%2C%20including%20Mr%20Stalin's%20DMK%2C%20have%20united%20to%20block%20the%20bill%2C%20which%20proposes%20changes%20to%20laws%20that%20decide%20how%20Muslim%20charitable%20properties%20are%20administered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20contended%20that%20the%20bill%20is%20unconstitutional%20and%20violates%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20practice%20religion%2C%20Article%2014%2C%20which%20guarantees%20equality%20before%20law%20and%20Article%2015%2C%20which%20bars%20discrimination%20on%20basis%20of%20religion.%20Sections%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20maintain%20the%20amendments%20are%20geared%20to%20help%20the%20government%20gain%20control%20of%20the%20Waqf%20properties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly%20has%20already%20passed%20a%20resolution%20to%20urge%20the%20Centre%20to%20withdraw%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%20today%2C%20Mr%20Stalin%20said%20the%20Constitution%20grants%20every%20citizen%20the%20right%20to%20follow%20their%20respective%20religion%20and%20it%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20elected%20governments%20to%20uphold%20and%20protect%20this%20right.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20proposed%20amendments%20in%20the%20bill%20have%20not%20taken%20that%20into%20consideration%20and%20the%20amended%20law%20is%20%26quot%3Bbound%20to%20severely%20harm%20the%20interest%20of%20Muslim%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20cited%20multiple%20points%20in%20his%20letter%20to%20cite%20how%20the%20bill%20can%20interfere%20with%20and%20undermine%20the%20religious%20autonomy%20of%20the%20Waqf%20boards%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Muslim%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20examples%2C%20he%20cited%20the%20proposed%20mandatory%20inclusion%20of%20two%20non-Muslim%20members%20in%20waqf%20boards.%20The%20removal%20of%20the%20'Waqf%20by%20user'%20provision%20threatens%20the%20status%20of%20many%20historical%20Waqf%20properties%2C%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stipulation%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bindividuals%20who%20practiced%20Islam%20for%20at%20least%20five%20years%20only%20can%20donate%20properties%20to%20Waqf%20will%20prevent%20non-Muslims%20from%20donating%20properties%20to%20Waqf%20which%20will%20hinder%20the%20syncretic%20culture%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20contended%20that%20the%20law%20is%20being%20amended%20to%20empower%20women%20and%20children%2C%20who%20have%20been%20suffering%20under%20the%20existing%20rules.%20The%20bill%20requires%20that%20money%20received%20by%20the%20Waqf%20Board%20must%20be%20used%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20widows%2C%20divorcees%2C%20and%20orphans%20in%20the%20manner%20suggested%20by%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%2C%20Union%20minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20religious%20sentiments...%20The%20role%20of%20Waqf%20boards%20is%20to%20supervise%20management%20of%20Waqf%20properties...%20this%20(the%20proposed%20law)%20is%20purely%20a%20provision%20for%20governance%20and%20supervision.%20It%20is%20simply%20a%20matter%20of%20property%20management%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rijiju%20also%20claimed%20that%20previously%20%26quot%3Bany%20land%20could%20be%20declared%20as%20Waqf%20property%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20removed%20that%20provision.%20This%20provision%20was%20misused%20to%20such%20an%20extent%20tha%20the%20number%20of%20properties%20increased%20to%20lakhs.%20Temples%20and%20gurdwaras%20had%20been%20claimed%20as%20Waqf%20land%20despite%20no%20records%20of%20mosques%20in%20those%20areas%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSurendereshwar%20Temple%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20was%20declared%20Waqf...%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20thousands%20of%20acres%20of%20land...%20in%20Haryana%2C%20a%20Sikh%20gurudwara%20was%20also%20declared%20Waqf%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743591300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F2ojubn7g_mk-stalin_625x300_22_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-amid-waqf-debate-in-parliament-mk-stalins-withdraw-bill-demand-to-pm-narendra-modi-8069299%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20has%20written%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20seeking%20his%20personal%20intervention%20to%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%20which%20was%20introduced%20in%20parliament%20today%20for%20debate%20and%20passing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-amid-waqf-debate-in-parliament-mk-stalins-withdraw-bill-demand-to-pm-narendra-modi-8069299%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20commuted%205%20hours%20a%20day%2C%203%20days%20a%20week%20for%20a%20year.%20I%20quit%20and%20pivoted%20my%20career%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20my%20daughter.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alexandra%20R.%20Kelly%20in%20a%20black%20leather%20jacket%20smiling%20for%20the%20camera%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e5bd1869253ccddf9a86c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlexandra%20Kelly%20now%20enjoys%20afterschool%20afternoons%20with%20her%20daughter.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alexandra%20R.%20Kelly%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20I%20was%20laid%20