nt%20clarity%20and%20advanced%20tracking%20metrics.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIndustry%20leaders%20say%20they%20want%20a%20unified%20podcast%20definition%20to%20help%20ensure%20future%20growth.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20knows%20precisely%20how%20to%20define%20what%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fpodcast%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epodcast%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20is%20anymore%20%E2%80%94%20and%20debate%20around%20the%20topic%20is%20roiling%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20%26quot%3Bpodcast%26quot%3B%20used%20to%20refer%20to%20an%20on-demand%20audio%20show%20of%20people%20discussing%20things%2C%20but%20that%20definition%20has%20become%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-eyeing-video-podcasts-creators-next-growth-act-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblurry%20over%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20half%20%E2%80%94%2052%25%20%E2%80%94%20of%20people%20now%20say%20videos%20that%20are%20%3Cem%3Eonly%3C%2Fem%3E%20available%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20be%20considered%20podcasts%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20report%20by%20Oxford%20Road%20and%20Edison%20Research%20aptly%20titled%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20Is%20a%20Podcast%3F%20Preserving%20its%20Essence%2C%20Structuring%20for%20Expansion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20popular%20definition%20in%20the%20survey%20%E2%80%94%20accepted%20by%2072%25%20%E2%80%94%20was%20recordings%20of%20people%20discussing%20a%20topic%20on%20YouTube%20that's%20also%20available%20as%20audio%20shows%20elsewhere%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotify-video-podcasts-creators-youtube-comparison-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpotify%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20Apple%20Podcasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20answers%20changed%20based%20on%20people's%20media%20habits.%20People%20were%20more%20willing%20to%20consider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-podcasts-earnings-video-donald-trump-neal-mohan-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube-only%20videos%20as%20podcasts%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20they'd%20listened%20to%20podcasts%2C%20and%20even%20more%20so%20if%20they'd%20watched%20video%20podcasts.%20Oxford%20Road%20and%20Edison%20Research%20surveyed%20more%20than%204%2C000%20Americans%2012%20and%20up%20for%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F2VyD3%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Definition%20of%20a%20podcast%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22553%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20is%20another%20sign%20of%20how%20the%20format's%20definition%20is%20shifting%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20not%20just%20an%20academic%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPodcasting%20has%20never%20been%20bigger.%20It's%20credited%20with%20helping%20shape%20the%20presidential%20election%2C%20and%20Big%20Tech%20is%20coming%20for%20its%20piece.%20YouTube%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Ffeed%2Fyoutube-podcast-listeners%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevealed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February%20that%20more%20than%201%20billion%20people%20every%20month%20listen%20to%20podcasts%20on%20the%20platform.%20Spotify%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20pushing%20into%20video.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencers-are-using-podcasts-to-reinvent-themselves-earn-more-money-2025-2https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencers-are-using-podcasts-to-reinvent-themselves-earn-more-money-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECreators%20are%20increasingly%3C%2Fa%3E%20getting%20into%20the%20medium%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20convergence%20of%20audio%20and%20video%20in%20the%20podcast%20medium%20has%20caused%20confusion%20and%20complexity%20for%20advertisers.%20Ad%20buyers%20now%20have%20to%20wrangle%20over%20which%20of%20their%20clients'%20budgets%20podcasting%20should%20come%20out%20of%20%E2%80%94%20audio%20or%20video%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20slowing%20down%20the%20ad-buying%20process%2C%20the%20report%20found.%20Platforms%20like%20Spotify%20and%20YouTube%20also%20make%20third-party%20tracking%20difficult%2C%20which%20means%20performance%20advertisers%20struggle%20to%20assess%20how%20their%20ads%20are%20performing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20there's%20lack%20of%20clarity%2C%20there's%20confusion%2C%20and%20there's%20frustration%2C%20and%20advertisers%20will%20take%20their%20business%20elsewhere%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dan%20Granger%2C%20CEO%20of%20Oxford%20Road%20and%20Veritone%20One%2C%20which%20helps%20marketers%20buy%20podcast%20ads.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20advertisers%20not%20buy%20shows%20because%20of%20this.%20It's%20material.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOxford%20Road%20and%20Edison's%20report%20calls%20for%20the%20podcast%20industry%20to%20agree%20on%20common%20definitions%20and%20explore%20the%20development%20of%20a%20system%20to%20measure%20podcasting%20across%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22df9b1b00-f8a3-4d97-b5e8-67c836366c2c%5C%22%3EVideo%20raises%20questions%20for%20hosts%2C%20too%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20to%20video%20has%20other%20consequences%20for%20podcasting.%20Uploading%20files%20as%20videos%20can%20make%20more%20money%20for%20the%20host%20and%20let%20advertisers%20reach%20a%20bigger%20audience%2C%20but%20it%20also%20creates%20more%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20good%20thing%20because%20it's%20pushing%20the%20industry%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jeff%20Umbro%2C%20CEO%20of%20The%20Podglomerate%2C%20which%20makes%2C%20markets%2C%20and%20monetizes%20podcasts%20for%20organizations%20like%20PBS%2C%20Netflix%2C%20and%20others.%20%26quot%3BI%20also%20think%20that%20nobody's%20really%20talking%20about%20the%20administrative%20burden%20that%20this%20adds%2C%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20reconcile%20all%20these%20payments%2C%20the%20time%20it%20takes%20to%20upload%20to%20all%20these%20platforms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20broadly%2C%20the%20shift%20raises%20identity%20questions%20for%20hosts.%20As%20they%20go%20beyond%20audio%20to%20video%2C%20and%20then%20do%20live%20events%20and%20sell%20ads%20on%20social%20media%2C%20they%20start%20to%20look%20more%20like%20influencers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoining%20the%20influencer%20club%20means%20potentially%20accessing%20a%20bigger%20ad%20pie.%20Advertisers%20spent%20%249.2%20billion%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.emarketer.com%2Fcontent%2Fus-influencer-marketing-forecast-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfluencer%20marketing%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202024%2C%20versus%20%242.3%20billion%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.emarketer.com%2Flearningcenter%2Fguides%2Fthe-podcast-industry-report-statistics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epodcast%20advertising%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20per%20EMARKETER.%20However%2C%20it%20could%20also%20distance%20them%20from%20the%20positive%20qualities%20that%20podcasting%20has%20become%20associated%20with%2C%20such%20as%20the%20intimate%20relationship%20hosts%20have%20with%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20hosts%20branch%20out%20to%20other%20things%2C%20it%20can%20also%20get%20complicated%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20share%20the%20resulting%20ad%20dollars%20among%20stakeholders.%20And%20there's%20the%20question%20of%20what%20happens%20to%20a%20podcast's%20value%20on%20YouTube.%20YouTube%20videos%20can%20command%20around%20a%20third%20of%20podcasts'%20ad%20rates%20because%20advertisers%20discount%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20viewing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteve%20Blackford%2C%20head%20of%20customer%20acquisition%20for%20LifeLock%2C%20a%20longtime%20podcast%20advertiser%2C%20said%20he's%20resigned%20to%20figuring%20out%20video%20advertising%20because%20that's%20where%20the%20audience%20is%20going.%20But%20it's%20hard%20to%20track%20an%20ad%20when%20it%20runs%20across%20both%20video%20and%20audio.%20Some%20podcasters%20sell%20video%20and%20audio%20together%20as%20a%20bundle%20and%20don't%20break%20out%20the%20audience%20by%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20performance%20marketer%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20put%20those%20all%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Blackford%20said.%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20I%20know%20what%20value%20I'm%20getting%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20players%20are%20trying%20to%20solve%20for%20the%20complexity.%20SiriusXM%20is%20rolling%20out%20Creator%20Connect%2C%20a%20tool%20that%20creates%20different%20versions%20of%20a%20podcast%20ad%20for%20video%20and%20social%20media.%20Gabe%20Tartaglia%2C%20who%20heads%20podcast%20and%20satellite%20sales%20for%20SiriusXM%2C%20said%20the%20company%20was%20hearing%20from%20advertisers%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20be%20able%20to%20buy%20against%20hosts'%20multiplatform%20efforts.%20About%2012%25%20of%20SiriusXM's%20podcast%20advertisers%20are%20already%20running%20ads%20on%20more%20than%20one%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpotify%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20it%20offers%20dynamic%20ad%20tools%20and%20works%20with%20third%20parties%20to%20support%20its%20podcast%20ad%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e50d4bac-06e8-42aa-af64-52debf4ff476%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20in%20a%20name%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report's%20authors%20interviewed%2030%20industry%20stakeholders%20and%20found%20a%20few%20common%20themes.%20Some%20said%20the%20audio%20element%20was%20primary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can%20mute%20it%20and%20it%20doesn't%20make%20sense%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20pod%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20Granger%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20said%20it%20didn't%20matter%20what%20platform%20it%20was%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20proposed%20a%20new%20definition%20for%20podcast%3A%20%26quot%3BAn%20on-demand%20audio-driven%20program%20featuring%20episodic%20content%20across%20wide-ranging%20themes%20and%20formats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%2C%20more%20simply%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20it%20works%20with%20your%20eyes%20closed%2C%20it's%20a%20podcast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20video%20podcast%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Ban%20episodic%2C%20on-demand%20program%20centered%20on%20spoken-word%20content%2C%20where%20synchronized%20visuals%20meaningfully%20shape%20the%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGranger%20said%20without%20a%20shared%20vocabulary%20that%20enables%20podcasting%20to%20be%20measured%20and%20clarified%20for%20advertisers%2C%20the%20industry%20risks%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvestment%20in%20the%20industry%20chases%20industry%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20they%20can't%20define%20it%2C%20you%20can't%20forecast%20it%2C%20and%20if%20you%20can't%20forecast%20it%2C%20institutional%20capital%20is%20less%20bullish%2C%20you%20have%20less%20growth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20said%20they%20wouldn't%20mind%20if%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bpodcast%26quot%3B%20went%20away%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20podcasting%20goes%20away%2C%20that's%20not%20a%20national%20tragedy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20quoted%20Ira%20Glass%2C%20host%20of%20%26quot%3BThis%20American%20Life%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20saying.%20%26quot%3BCreative%20people%20will%20find%20a%20place%20to%20make%20stuff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20view%20is%20that%20the%20industry%20shouldn't%20abandon%20a%20term%20that%20has%20earned%20strong%20credibility%20with%20advertisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20area%20of%20agreement%20seems%20to%20be%20that%20video%20isn't%20going%20away%20as%20a%20format%20for%20podcasts%2C%20especially%20with%20YouTube%20making%20a%20big%20play%20for%20them.%20YouTube's%20role%20is%20poised%20to%20get%20even%20larger%20if%20it%20gets%20into%20dynamic%20ad%20insertion%2C%20as%20Semafor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.semafor.com%2Farticle%2F03%2F23%2F2025%2Fhow-a-technical-tweak-to-youtubes-ads-could-transform-podcasting%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20it's%20looking%20into.%20This%20would%20allow%20for%20more%20customization%20and%20potentially%20trackability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frise-of-video-podcasts-complications-confusion-advertisers-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743589801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ec168663d72727e198d5d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frise-of-video-podcasts-complications-confusion-advertisers-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20half%20of%20people%20consider%20videos%20only%20available%20on%20YouTube%20to%20be%20a%20podcast%2C%20a%20new%20report%20found.%20That%20makes%20it%20complicated%20for%20advertisers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lmoses%40insider.com%20(Lucia%20Moses)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frise-of-video-podcasts-complications-confusion-advertisers-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Forbes%202025%3A%20How%20Donald%20Trump%20Doubled%20His%20Net%20Worth%20In%20A%20Year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20secured%20the%20700th%20spot%20on%20the%202025%20Forbes%20Billionaires%20List.%20Once%20facing%20a%20precarious%20future%20with%20mounting%20legal%20troubles%20and%20financial%20setbacks%2C%20Trump%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20his%20net%20worth%20in%20just%20a%20year%2C%20surging%20from%20%242.3%20billion%20to%20%245.1%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2078-year-old%20first%20appeared%20on%20the%20inaugural%20Forbes%20400%20list%20in%201982%20alongside%20his%20father%2C%20Fred%20Trump%2C%20with%20a%20combined%20estimated%20fortune%20of%20%24200%20million.%20His%20wealth%20has%20always%20been%20rooted%20in%20real%20estate%2C%20but%20recent%20years%20saw%20challenges%20in%20the%20sector%20due%20to%20rising%20interest%20rates%2C%20a%20shift%20to%20online%20shopping%2C%20and%20the%20decline%20of%20office%20spaces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20owning%20golf%20courses%2C%20luxury%20properties%2C%20a%20winery%2C%20and%20a%20Boeing%20757%20nicknamed%20'Trump%20Force%20One'%2C%20Trump%20faced%20serious%20financial%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20that%2C%20a%20New%20York%20court%20ordered%20Trump%20to%20pay%20%24454%20million%20in%20penalties%20after%20he%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20inflating%20his%20net%20worth%20to%20secure%20better%20credit%20terms.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20New%20York%20Attorney%20General%20Letitia%20James%20even%20hinted%20at%20seizing%20Trump's%20assets%2C%20including%20the%2040%20Wall%20Street%20building.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20managed%20to%20delay%20enforcement%2C%20successfully%20arguing%20for%20a%20reduced%20bond%20of%20%24175%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire%20managed%20to%20boost%20his%20finances%20when%20he%20decided%20to%20take%20Truth%20Social's%20parent%20company%20public.%20Despite%20the%20platform's%20modest%20revenue%20and%20significant%20losses%2C%20investors%20-%20many%20of%20them%20Trump%20loyalists%20-%20drove%20its%20stock%20to%20astronomical%20levels.%20Though%20shares%20later%20fell%20by%2072%20per%20cent%2C%20Trump%20still%20held%20a%20%242.6%20billion%20stake%20as%20of%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20social%20media%2C%20Trump%20capitalised%20on%20his%20influence%20by%20selling%20everything%20from%20NFTs%20(non-fungible%20tokens)%20and%20coffee-table%20books%20to%20sneakers%20and%20Bibles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Trump's%20most%20unexpected%20windfall%20came%20from%20the%20cryptocurrency%20world.%C2%A0Late%20last%20year%2C%20he%20launched%20World%20Liberty%20Financial%2C%20a%20crypto%20project%20targeting%20novice%20investors.%20Initially%20overlooked%2C%20the%20venture%20exploded%20after%20Trump%20won%20the%20presidential%20election%2C%20with%20hype%20from%20crypto%20entrepreneur%20Justin%20Sun%20generating%20an%20estimated%20%24245%20million%20after%20taxes%20for%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20stopping%20there%2C%20the%20billionaire%20introduced%20%24TRUMP%2C%20a%20digital%20token%20that%20openly%20embraced%20speculative%20trading.%20The%20move%20generated%20roughly%20%24350%20million%20in%20fees%2C%20with%20Trump's%20estimated%20share%20reaching%20at%20least%20%24110%20million%20after%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20still%20owing%20around%20%24500%20million%20in%20legal%20penalties%2C%20Trump%20now%20has%20an%20estimated%20%24800%20million%20in%20liquid%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Forbes%202025%20Billionaires%20List%20has%20a%20record-breaking%203%2C028%20billionaires%20with%20a%20collective%20net%20worth%20of%20%2416.1%20trillion.%20At%20the%20top%20of%20the%20list%20is%20Donald%20Trump's%20close%20advisor%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20with%20an%20estimated%20fortune%20of%20%24342%20billion.%20Musk%2C%20who%20leads%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%2C%20retains%20his%20position%20as%20the%20world's%20richest%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743589500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Ffr2uug4k_donald-trump-oval-office-afp_625x300_01_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fforbes-billionaire-list-elon-musk-fred-trump-forbes-2025-how-donald-trump-doubled-his-net-worth-in-a-year-8068974%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20first%20appeared%20on%20the%20inaugural%20Forbes%20400%20list%20in%201982%20alongside%20his%20father%20with%20a%20combined%20estimated%20fortune%20of%20%24200%20million%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fforbes-billionaire-list-elon-musk-fred-trump-forbes-2025-how-donald-trump