dias-richest-woman-with-over-35-5-billion-net-worth-8068351%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Can%20Studio%20Ghibli%20Sue%20OpenAI%20Over%20AI-Generated%20Images%3F%20What%20Lawyer%20Says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStudio%20Ghibli%20may%20have%20legal%20grounds%20to%20take%20action%20against%20OpenAI%20over%20ChatGPT's%20AI-generated%20images%2C%20a%20legal%20expert%20has%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Japanese%20animation%20studio%20could%20%26quot%3Bclaim%20OpenAI%20has%20violated%20the%20Lanham%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20Rob%C2%A0Rosenberg%2C%20founder%20of%20Telluride%20Legal%20Strategies%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffuturism.com%2Flawyer-studio-ghibli-legal-action-openai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFuturism%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lanham%20Act%2C%20a%20federal%20law%20enacted%20in%201946%2C%20governs%20trademark%20protection%2C%20false%20advertising%2C%20and%20unfair%20competition.%20It%20allows%20businesses%20to%20sue%20over%20unauthorised%20use%20of%20their%20branding%20or%20style%20that%20could%20mislead%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGhibli%20could%20argue%20that%20by%20converting%20user%20photos%20to%20'Ghibli-style%2C'%20OpenAI%20is%20trading%20off%20the%20goodwill%20of%20Ghibli's%20trademarks%2C%20using%20its%20recognisable%20artistic%20identity%20in%20a%20way%20that%20may%20confuse%20consumers%20into%20believing%20the%20function%20is%20endorsed%20or%20licensed%20by%20the%20studio%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rosenberg%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20OpenAI%20could%20face%20legal%20challenges%20for%20training%20its%20AI%20models%20on%20copyrighted%20works%20belonging%20to%20Studio%20Ghibli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20week%20or%20so%2C%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20users%20have%20flooded%20social%20media%20with%20Studio%20Ghibli-inspired%20AI-generated%20images.%20The%20surge%20forced%20OpenAI%20to%20impose%20restrictions%2C%20with%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20saying%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Four-gpus-are-melting-sam-altman-says-openai-to-limit-chatgpt-image-generation-requests-studio-ghibli-ai-art-trend-8038362%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGPUs%20were%20%26quot%3Bmelting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20led%20to%20debates%20on%20copyright%20infringement%20and%20the%20ethics%20of%20AI-generated%20content%2C%20especially%20its%20impact%20on%20human%20artists%2C%20including%20Studio%20Ghibli's%20animators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rosenberg%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20outcome%20of%20any%20potential%20lawsuit%20remains%20uncertain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20OpenAI%20were%20marketing%20its%20platform%20as%20a%20place%20where%20consumers%20could%20transform%20their%20photos%20into%20'Ghibli-style'%20anime%2C%20that%20fact%20would%20weigh%20more%20strongly%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20court%20finding%20that%20OpenAI's%20conduct%20violated%20the%20Lanham%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20courts%20reject%20OpenAI's%20fair%20use%20argument%2C%20Mr%20Rosenberg%20speculated%20that%20AI%20developers%20may%20have%20to%20compensate%20copyright%20holders%20and%20credit%20them%20for%20influencing%20AI-generated%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20clear%20legal%20precedent%20exists%20on%20whether%20OpenAI%20has%20violated%20US%20copyright%20law.%20The%20company%20argues%20that%20training%20its%20models%20falls%20under%20%26quot%3Bfair%20use%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20key%20point%20in%20AI%20copyright%20debates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20copyright%20concerns%2C%20the%20controversy%20could%20also%20impact%20Studio%20Ghibli's%20ability%20to%20monetise%20its%20signature%20art%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Studio%20Ghibli%20ever%20wanted%20to%20launch%20its%20own%20tool%20allowing%20fans%20to%20transform%20photos%20into%20its%20signature%20style%2C%20OpenAI's%20update%20has%20essentially%20taken%20that%20business%20opportunity%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rosenberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20more%20concerning%2C%20he%20added%2C%20was%20the%20possibility%20that%20AI%20could%20generate%20entire%20animations%20in%20the%20Ghibli%20style%2C%20misleading%20audiences%20into%20believing%20they%20were%20official%20works.%20It%20blurs%20%26quot%3Bthe%20line%20between%20homage%20and%20outright%20misrepresentation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743585120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fmv1ijsc8_ghiblistyle-art-meme_625x300_02_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fstudio-ghibli-may-have-grounds-to-sue-openai-over-ai-art-lawyer-8067470%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20lawyer%20said%20that%20OpenAI%20could%20face%20legal%20challenges%20for%20training%20its%20AI%20models%20on%20copyrighted%20works%20belonging%20to%20Studio%20Ghibli%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fstudio-ghibli-may-have-grounds-to-sue-openai-over-ai-art-lawyer-8067470%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bengaluru%20Airport%E2%80%99s%20New%20Sensory%20Room%20Is%20Making%20Travel%20Easier%20for%20Everyone%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20global%20awareness%20of%20neurodivergence%20rises%2C%20many%20public%20spaces%2C%20including%20airports%2C%20are%20starting%20to%20accommodate%20the%20unique%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F417379%2Fmugdha-kalra-shares-parenting-methods-raising-autistic-child-world-autism-awareness-day%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eneeds%20of%20neurodivergent%20individuals%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20approximately%201%20in%2068%20children%