investment%20operations%20at%20Arvest%20Bank%20Group%2C%20Ms%20Walton%20worked%20as%20an%20equity%20analyst%20and%20money%20manager%20for%20First%20Commerce%20Corporation.%20She%20worked%20as%20a%20broker%20for%20EF%20Hutton%20as%20well.%20In%201988%2C%20Ms%20Walton%20established%20the%20investment%20bank%20Llama%20Company%2C%20where%20she%20served%20as%20its%20president%2C%20chair%2C%20and%20chief%20executive%20officer.%20It%20was%20closed%20after%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20the%20development%20of%20the%20Northwest%20Arkansas%20Regional%20Airport%20and%20was%20the%20first%20person%20to%20chair%20the%20Northwest%20Arkansas%20Council.%20As%20the%20new%20airport%20required%20%24109%20million%2C%20Ms%20Walton%20personally%20gave%20%2415%20million%2C%20and%20her%20company%2C%20Llama%20Company%2C%20helped%20raise%20%2479.5%20million%20through%20bonds.%20The%20main%20terminal%20of%20the%20airport%20has%20been%20named%20after%20her%20to%20honour%20her%20efforts.%20It's%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BAlice%20L.%20Walton%20Terminal%20Building.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20never%20actively%20participated%20in%20Walmart's%20operation%2C%20instead%20preferring%20to%20concentrate%20on%20her%20own%20business%20endeavours%20and%20eventually%20becoming%20a%20patron%20of%20art.%20She%20spends%20her%20wealth%20on%20everything%20from%20horse%20breeding%20to%20pricey%20artwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20was%2010%20years%20old%2C%20Walton%20paid%20%242%20for%20her%20first%20piece%20of%20art.%20It%20was%20a%20replica%20of%20a%20painting%20by%20Picasso.%20She%20even%20established%20a%20%2450%20million%20museum%20in%202011%20called%20the%20Crystal%20Bridges%20Museum%20of%20American%20Art%20in%20Bentonville%2C%20Arkansas%2C%20to%20house%20her%20art%20collection%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20valued%20at%20over%20%24500%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20Forbes%20report%2C%20she%20has%20also%20previously%20contributed%20to%20Republican%20candidates%20and%20political%20action%20committees.%20In%202016%2C%20though%2C%20she%20gave%20%24353%2C400%20to%20the%20Hillary%20Victory%20Fund%2C%20a%20joint%20fundraising%20group%20that%20supports%20Clinton%20and%20other%20Democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743583980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fjm9mjma8_alice-walton_625x300_27_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fforbes-billionaire-list-2025-who-is-alice-walton-worlds-richest-woman-with-102-billion-fortune-8068236%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20a%20%24102%20billion%20fortune%2C%20Walmart%20heir%20Alice%20Walton%20is%20the%20richest%20woman%20on%20the%20Forbes%20Billionaire%20List%202025.%20Ms%20Walton%2C%2075%2C%20overtook%20French%20L'Oreal%20heiress%20Francoise%20Bettencourt%20Meyers%2C%20who%20held%20the%20title%20last%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fforbes-billionaire-list-2025-who-is-alice-walton-worlds-richest-woman-with-102-billion-fortune-8068236%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Unprecedented%20CCP%20shake-up%3A%20Xi%E2%80%99s%20inner%20circle%20gets%20a%20jolt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743583378000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119901002%2Cimgsize-20034.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchinese-president-xi-jinping-china-communist-party-reshuffle-ccp-politburo-role-swap%2Farticleshow%2F119900973.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F119900973.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EChinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20has%20unexpectedly%20swapped%20roles%20of%20Politburo%20members%20Li%20Ganjie%20and%20Shi%20Taifeng.%20This%20signif