%2Fjyoti-padma-dairy-farming-cow-currency-a2-milk-ownership-lactose-intolerance%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintroduced%20me%20to%20A2%20milk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20was%20curious%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20She%20found%20that%20A2%20milk%20is%20easier%20to%20digest%20and%20has%20fewer%20negative%20effects%2C%20especially%20for%20people%20with%20PCOS%E2%80%94a%20condition%20she%20had%20been%20struggling%20with%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Pronobesh%20Ganguly%2C%20a%20gynaecologist%20and%20obstetrician%20from%20West%20Bengal%2C%20explains%20why%20A2%20milk%20stands%20out.%20%E2%80%9CA2%20milk%2C%20rich%20in%20A2%20beta-casein%20and%20free%20from%20A1%20beta-casein%2C%20helps%20prevent%20the%20release%20of%20BCM-7%2C%20a%20peptide%20found%20in%20regular%20cow%E2%80%99s%20milk.%20This%20makes%20digestion%20smoother%20for%20many%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20it%20all%20clicked.%20What%20if%20she%20could%20combine%20the%20goodness%20of%20Greek%20yoghurt%20with%20the%20benefits%20of%20A2%20milk%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFinding%20purpose%3A%20From%20IT%20professional%20to%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Harshita%20started%20working%20at%20Four-Serv%20Global.%20Although%20she%20was%20performing%20well%2C%20she%20felt%20unfulfilled%20and%20realised%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20path%20she%20wanted%20to%20pursue.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20of%20my%20own%2C%20something%20that%20aligned%20with%20my%20values%20and%20goals%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC00164-1_11zon-1743132374-500x625.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20young%20entrepreneur%20wanted%20to%20