h%20care%20and%20respect%20for%20the%20cultural%20and%20spiritual%20significance%20of%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandip%20credits%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Exposition%20to%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20team%20behind%20it.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20one-person%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20need%20a%20team%20of%20dedicated%20professionals%20who%20can%20take%20charge%20of%20their%20respective%20areas%20and%20work%20together%20towards%20a%20common%20goal.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EExperience%20with%20large-scale%20events%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20not%20the%20first%20time%20the%20IAS%20officer%20was%20tasked%20with%20managing%20a%20large-scale%20event.%20In%202013-14%2C%20as%20the%20Executive%20Director%20of%20the%20Sports%20Authority%20of%20Goa%2C%20he%20was%20given%20the%20responsibility%20of%20overseeing%20the%20Lusofonia%20Games%2C%20a%20multi-sport%20event%20for%20Portuguese-speaking%20nations.%20%E2%80%9COrganising%20an%20event%20of%20such%20magnitude%20is%20always%20a%20challenge.%20But%20with%20the%20right%20team%20and%20resources%2C%20it%20becomes%20a%20rewarding%20experience%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lusofonia%20Games%2C%20which%20brought%20together%20countries%20like%20Brazil%2C%20Portugal%2C%20and%20Zimbabwe%2C%20could%20be%20likened%20to%20a%20mini-Olympics%20held%20in%20the%20State%20of%20Goa.%20The%20event%20was%20especially%20significant%20due%20to%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20historical%20ties%20with%20the%20Portuguese%20regime%2C%20as%20it%20was%20once%20part%20of%20the%20Portuguese%20empire%2C%20and%20many%20people%20in%20the%20region%20speak%20Portuguese.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FSt-Francis-Xavier-Feast-Old-Goa-2-1-2-1743089652.jpg%5C%